::DeathScythe::

DeathScythe turns his head as he feels the gun shoved into his mouth, the 
shots only taking out several teeth. He growls, running off after Hot Rod.

He stops as he sees the ship's defences. DeathScythe turns around. One bot 
wasn't worth getting himself killed over. The assassin starts out on a run 
north, away from the ship.
